text:
e="preserve">Lynlee Smith (born 13 September 1987) is a New Zealand water polo player. She is a member of the New Zealand women's national water polo team. She played at the 2009 World Aquatics Championships and 2013 World Aquatics Championships.
She was born in Auckland. She was educated at Westlake Girls High School. She played for Arizona State University's women's water polo team.
